<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: right"><font style="TEXT-DECORATION: underline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold">EXHIBIT 99.3</font></div>

<div>&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><img src="mm11-1215_scto992top.jpg" alt=""><br>
<div>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="82%" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Attached please find the Kroger-Roundy&#8217;s Merger <font style="DISPLAY: inline">Discussion Guide</font> and <font style="DISPLAY: inline">Q&amp;A</font>.</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font size="3">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<hr style="COLOR: royalblue" align="left" noshade size="1" width="100%">
</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font color="royalblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">The Kroger Co. and Roundy&#8217;s, Inc., today announced a merger agreement that would expand Kroger&#8217;s footprint to include complementary supermarkets in Wisconsin and 34 Mariano&#8217;s locations in Chicago.</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<hr style="COLOR: royalblue" align="left" noshade size="1" width="100%">
</div>
</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Key Points</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline"><font style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">About Roundy&#8217;s: </font>&#160;Based in Milwaukee, Roundy&#8217;s has more than 22,000 associates who work in and support 151 stores in the greater Chicago area and in Wisconsin. These supermarkets include 34 Mariano&#8217;s stores in Chicago and 117 stores in Wisconsin operating under three banners: Pick &#8216;n Save, Copps and Metro Market. Roundy&#8217;s also operates two distribution centers and one commissary, all in Wisconsin.</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font size="3">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline"><font style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Terms:</font>&#160; As part of the agreement, Kroger will purchase all outstanding shares of Roundy&#8217;s for $3.60 per share in cash. The transaction is valued at approximately $800 million, including debt.</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Together, we will have more than 422,000 associates who serve customers in 2,774 stores in 35 states and the District of Columbia.&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font size="3">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<hr style="COLOR: royalblue" align="left" noshade size="1" width="100%">
</div>
</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">About This Merger</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">&#8220;We are so excited to welcome Roundy&#8217;s to the Kroger family. With a team of more than 22,000 talented associates, outstanding store locations and a shared commitment to putting customers first, Roundy&#8217;s has a lot of opportunity for growth. &#8230; Together, we are committed to investing in Roundy&#8217;s people, communities, stores and merchandising to deliver a fantastic customer experience that will create opportunities for associates, grow customer loyalty and revenue, and create value for shareholders.&#8221;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font size="3">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline"><font style="FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">&#8213;</font><font style="FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Rodney McMullen, Kroger Chairman &amp; CEO</font></font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<hr style="COLOR: royalblue" align="left" noshade size="1" width="100%">
</div>
</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Next Steps</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger will commence an offer to acquire the outstanding shares of Roundy&#8217;s. We would expect to close the transaction by the end of the calendar year. The transaction is subject to at least 50.1% of Roundy&#8217;s outstanding shares being tendered to Kroger and other customary conditions. For now, both Kroger- and Roundy&#8217;s-operated stores will continue to operate as usual until the merger transaction closes and we are ready to move forward with plans to integrate our operations. After closing, we will keep leaders and associates informed of our key integration steps and progress on an ongoing basis.</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font size="3">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<hr style="COLOR: royalblue" align="left" noshade size="1" width="100%">
</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Overview</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">&#8220;We are confident that with our scale, loyalty programs and strong balance sheet, combined with the capable, knowledgeable Roundy&#8217;s associates and superior store locations, we can grow the Wisconsin markets. At the same time, we are excited to learn about and leverage key findings from Mariano&#8217;s experiences in Chicago.&#8221;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font size="3">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;&#8211; <font style="FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Mike Schlotman, Kroger Executive Vice President &amp; CFO</font></font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<hr style="COLOR: royalblue" align="left" noshade size="1" width="100%">
</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><img src="mm11-1215_scto992logo.jpg" alt=""></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>
</div>
</td>
</tr><tr>
<td valign="top" width="82%" style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Additional Information and Where to Find It</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; DISPLAY: inline">The tender offer referenced herein has not yet commenced. This communication is for informational purposes only and is neither an offer to purchase nor a solicitation of an offer to sell shares of Roundy&#8217;s, Inc. (&#8220;Roundy&#8217;s&#8221;), nor is it a substitute for the tender offer materials that The Kroger Co. (&#8220;Parent&#8221;) and KS Merger Sub Inc. (&#8220;Acquisition Sub&#8221;), a wholly-owned subsidiary of Parent, will file with the Securities and Exchange Commission (&#8220;SEC&#8221;) upon commencement of the tender offer. At the time the tender offer is commenced, Parent and Acquisition Sub will file with the SEC tender offer materials on Schedule TO, and Roundy&#8217;s will file with the SEC a Solicitation/Recommendation Statement on Schedule 14D-9, with respect to the tender offer. The tender offer materials (including an Offer to Purchase, a related Letter of Transmittal and certain other tender offer documents) and the Solicitation/Recommendation Statement will contain important information. Holders of shares of Roundy&#8217;s are urged to read these documents carefully when they become available, because they will contain important information that holders of Roundy&#8217;s securities should consider before making any decision regarding tendering their securities. The Offer to Purchase, the related Letter of Transmittal and certain other tender offer documents, as well as the Solicitation/Recommendation Statement, will be made available to all holders of shares of Roundy&#8217;s at no expense to them. The tender offer materials and the Solicitation/Recommendation Statement will be made available for free at the SEC&#8217;s web site at <font style="DISPLAY: inline">www.sec.gov</font>. Additional copies of the tender offer materials may be obtained at no charge by sending a written request to Parent at The Kroger Co., 1014 Vine Street, Cincinnati, OH 45202-1100, Attention: General Counsel.</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font size="3">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Forward-Looking Statements</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">This document contains certain forward-looking statements about the future performance of Kroger. These statements are based on management's assumptions and beliefs in light of the information currently available to it. These statements are indicated by words such as "expect," "intend," "guidance,&#8221; &#8220;will" and similar words.&#160; Various uncertainties and other factors could cause actual results to differ materially from those contained in the forward-looking statements. These include the specific risk factors identified in "Risk Factors" and "Outlook" in Kroger&#8217;s annual report on Form 10-K for our last fiscal year and any subsequent filings, as well as the following:</font></div>
</td>
</tr></table>
</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><br>
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 36pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: symbol, serif; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">&#183;</font><font id="TAB2" style="COLOR: black; LETTER-SPACING: 9pt">&#160; </font><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger&#8217;s ability to achieve sales, earnings and cash flow goals may be affected by: labor negotiations or disputes; changes in the types and numbers of businesses that compete with Kroger; pricing and promotional activities of existing and new competitors, including non-traditional competitors, and the aggressiveness of that competition; Kroger&#8217;s response to these actions; the state of the economy, including interest rates, the inflationary and deflationary trends in certain commodities, and the unemployment rate; the effect that fuel costs have on consumer spending; volatility of fuel margins; changes in government-funded benefit programs; manufacturing commodity costs; diesel fuel costs related to Kroger&#8217;s logistics operations; trends in consumer spending; the extent to which Kroger&#8217;s customers exercise caution in their purchasing in response to economic conditions; the inconsistent pace of the economic recovery; changes in inflation or deflation in product and operating costs; stock repurchases; Kroger&#8217;s ability to retain pharmacy sales from third party payors; consolidation in the healthcare industry, including pharmacy benefit managers; Kroger&#8217;s ability to negotiate modifications to multi-employer pension plans; natural disasters or adverse weather conditions; the potential costs and risks associated with potential cyber-attacks or data security breaches; the success of Kroger&#8217;s future growth plans; and the successful integration of Harris Teeter and Roundy&#8217;s.&#160; Kroger&#8217;s ability to achieve sales and earnings goals may also be affected by Kroger&#8217;s ability to manage the factors identified above.</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 36pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: symbol, serif; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">&#183;</font><font id="TAB2" style="COLOR: black; LETTER-SPACING: 9pt">&#160; </font><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger&#8217;s ability to use cash flow to continue to repurchase shares, fund dividends, increase capital investments, and maintain Kroger&#8217;s investment grade debt rating could be affected by unanticipated increases in net total debt, Kroger&#8217;s inability to generate cash flow at the levels anticipated, and Kroger&#8217;s failure to generate expected earnings.</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 36pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: symbol, serif; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">&#183;</font><font id="TAB2" style="COLOR: black; LETTER-SPACING: 9pt">&#160; </font><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger&#8217;s commencement of a tender offer will be contingent upon the merger agreement not being terminated prior to the commencement of the offer.&#160; The requirement to consummate the merger will be contingent upon the merger agreement being in effect and the conditions to the merger being satisfied or waived.&#160; The closing of the transaction could fail to occur before the end of calendar year 2015 if the tender offer does not achieve the anticipated results, if the conditions to closing are not satisfied or are not satisfied in a timely manner, or if the merger agreement is terminated as provided in the agreement.</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 36pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: symbol, serif; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">&#183;</font><font id="TAB2" style="COLOR: black; LETTER-SPACING: 9pt">&#160; </font><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger&#8217;s ability to finance the transaction with debt will depend on the availability of the debt markets, including commercial paper, our credit facility, and other sources of debt financing.</font></div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger assumes no obligation to update the information contained herein. Please refer to Kroger's reports and filings with the Securities and Exchange Commission for a further discussion of these risks and uncertainties.</font></div>
</div>

<DESCRIPTION>EX.99.4 - QUESTIONS & ANSWERS FOR ROUNDY?S
<TEXT>

<div>&#160;</div>

<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: right"><font style="TEXT-DECORATION: underline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold">EXHIBIT 99.4</font><br>
</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: Cambria; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: Cambria"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: Cambria">Kroger &amp; Roundy&#8217;s Announce <font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: Cambria">Merger Agreement</font></font></font></font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font>

<div>
<hr style="COLOR: black" align="center" noshade size="2" width="100%">
</div>
</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Questions &amp; Answers for Roundy&#8217;s Associates</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">November 11, 2015</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="royalblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Today&#8217;s News</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">We are pleased to announce that The Kroger Co. and Roundy&#8217;s, Inc., have signed an agreement to form a merger of the two companies. Roundy&#8217;s, based in Milwaukee, has more than 22,000 associates who work in and support 151 stores in the greater Chicago area and in Wisconsin.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">These Roundy&#8217;s supermarkets include 34 Mariano&#8217;s stores in greater Chicago, and 117 stores in Wisconsin operating under three banners: Pick &#8216;n Save, Copps and Metro Market. Roundy&#8217;s also operates two distribution centers and one commissary &#8211; all located in Wisconsin.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Together, Kroger and Roundy&#8217;s will operate 2,774 supermarkets and employ more than 422,000 associates across 35 states and the District of Columbia.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="royalblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Questions &amp; An<font color="royalblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">sw</font>ers</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">What happens next?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger will commence an offer to acquire the outstanding shares of Roundy&#8217;s. We would expect to close the transaction by the end of the calendar year. The transaction is subject to at least 50.1% of Roundy&#8217;s outstanding shares being tendered to Kroger and other customary conditions. For now, both Kroger<font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">-</font> and Roundy&#8217;s-operated stores will continue to operate as usual until the merger transaction closes and we are ready to move forward with plans to integrate our operations. After closing, we will keep leaders and associates informed of our key integration steps and progress on an ongoing basis.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Why did Kroger want to merge with Roundy&#8217;s?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Roundy&#8217;s brings to Kroger an expanded footprint with a complementary base of 151 stores and 101 pharmacies in new markets<font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">,</font> including Milwaukee, Madison and Northern Wisconsin, which are served under the Pick &#8216;n Save, Copps and Metro Market banners. The merger also provides Kroger with a stronger presence in the Chicagoland grocery market, where Roundy&#8217;s operates 34 stores under the Mariano&#8217;s banner.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">What will Kroger bring to Roundy&#8217;s?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger&#8217;s scale and financial strength will help Roundy&#8217;s invest in its home state of Wisconsin while continuing to grow in Chicago. We are committed to investing in Roundy&#8217;s people, stores and merchandising to deliver a fantastic customer experience that will increase customer loyalty and grow the business.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Why do we think this merger will be successful?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger has a long history of successfully integrating with our merger partners, sharing the best of what each company has to offer while maintaining and enhancing the culture that made each great. We did this during the merger with Dillons in 1983, with Fred Meyer in 1999<font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">,</font> and </font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>

<div id="PGBRK" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<div id="FTR">
<div id="GLFTR" style="WIDTH: 100%" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#160; </font></div>
</div>

<div id="PN" style="WIDTH: 100%; PAGE-BREAK-AFTER: always">
<div style="WIDTH: 100%; TEXT-ALIGN: right"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">11/11/15&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;The Kroger Co. Confidential&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;1</font></div>

<div style="WIDTH: 100%; TEXT-ALIGN: center">
<hr style="COLOR: indianred" noshade size="2">
</div>
</div>

<div id="HDR">
<div id="GLHDR" style="WIDTH: 100%" align="right"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#160; </font></div>
</div>
</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">most recently with Harris Teeter in 2014. Learning from each other and combining the best of each company has been the cornerstone of success in the mergers we have done through the years. We look forward to the same success with Roundy&#8217;s.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Our goal in this process is to support the continued success of Roundy&#8217;s and Kroger as we combine our companies. We believe that this merger will strengthen both of our organizations and deepen our connections with our customers and communities. At the same time, we are excited to welcome more than 22,000 Roundy&#8217;s associates to the Kroger family of companies. We look forward to working together to serve our customers, and to learning much from each other as partners in the coming weeks and months.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">How will Roundy&#8217;s operate its stores as part of Kroger?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">After the transaction closes, Roundy&#8217;s will continue to operate its stores as a subsidiary of The Kroger Co. and will continue to be led by Bob Mariano, its current president and CEO.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Will the headquarters location change?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Roundy&#8217;s will continue to operate from its current headquarters office in Milwaukee.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">When will we begin plans to integrate operations?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Stores in Kroger&#8217;s family of companies and Roundy&#8217;s will continue to operate as usual while we wait for completion of the tender offer and customary approvals. The merger is expected to close by the end of the calendar year.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">How long will the integration process take place?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Our integration efforts will begin after closing. While we do not have a specific time frame for completion, it is important to note that Kroger has a strong history of patiently working to achieve integration and synergy goals, which set the stage for long-term growth.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Do any markets have both Kroger and Roundy&#8217;s stores?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">In Chicago, Kroger operates 13 Food 4 Less price impact warehouse stores and Roundy&#8217;s operates 34 Mariano&#8217;s stores.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Will we change the Roundy&#8217;s banner names?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">We have no plans to change banner names at this time.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Will Roundy&#8217;s stores start carrying Kroger brand products?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Roundy&#8217;s will continue to carry Roundy&#8217;s brands. After the merger closes, teams from both organizations will come together to develop Merchandising plans and capture the best of both companies.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Will Roundy&#8217;s still offer double coupons?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger&#8217;s coupon policy is determined at the division level, and Roundy&#8217;s has indicated it has no plans to change its current coupon policies.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div id="PGBRK" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<div id="FTR">
<div id="GLFTR" style="WIDTH: 100%" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#160; </font></div>
</div>

<div style="WIDTH: 100%; TEXT-ALIGN: right"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">11/11/15&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;The Kroger Co. Confidential&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;2</font></div>

<div style="WIDTH: 100%; TEXT-ALIGN: center">
<hr style="COLOR: indianred" noshade size="2">
</div>
</div>

<div id="HDR">
<div id="GLHDR" style="WIDTH: 100%" align="right"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#160; </font></div>
</div>
</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">What should we tell customers who have questions?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Please emphasize that our Kroger team is excited to expand our family of companies, and we are committed to providing excellent service, selection and value, as always. We know that Roundy&#8217;s is similarly committed. Customers with questions are welcome to contact Kroger at 1-800-KROGERS at any time.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="royalblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">My Job, Pay &amp; Benefits</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Could some stores close eventually?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">We have no plans to close stores, and Roundy&#8217;s associates will continue to have employment opportunities with the company.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="midnightblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Will the distribution &amp; commissary facilities in Wisconsin remain open?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Yes, the Roundy&#8217;s distribution centers in Oconomowoc and Mazomanie, Wis., and the commissary in Kenosha, Wis., will continue to operate as usual.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Will there be layoffs as a result of this merger?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger believes our associates are the most important part of our company. We are excited to welcome Roundy&#8217;s associates to the Kroger family, and we will continue to rely on their talent and expertise to serve shoppers every day. We do not anticipate any layoffs as a result of this merger at this time. As we move through the integration process during the next several months, it is possible that there will be limited duplication of efforts in some functional areas. We will be in a position to learn and share more on an ongoing basis after the merger closes.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Will there be career opportunities at other locations?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger is a large organization with tremendous opportunities across many retail and functional areas in 34 states and the District of Columbia. We promote growth and change at all levels in the organization &#8211; we call this our &#8216;opportunity culture&#8217; &#8211; and we are always looking for and finding opportunities for talented individuals.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">If I&#8217;m an associate in a collective bargaining unit, how will the merger affect my compensation and benefits?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Post-closing, your compensation and benefits will continue to be governed by the terms and provisions of your collective bargaining agreement in place today.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">How will the merger affect other associates&#8217; compensation and benefits?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Under the merger agreement, your base salary or regular wages will not be decreased, and the overall value of your compensation and benefits after closing will remain comparable to what you have today, or comparable to a Kroger associate in a similar position, for a period of at least 18 months.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="darkblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">If I have any other pay, benefits or Human Resources questions, what should I do?</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">If you have additional questions about the merger at this time, please email <font color="blue" style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; TEXT-DECORATION: underline; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Employee.Communication@roundy&#8217;s.com</font>.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div id="PGBRK" style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">
<div id="FTR">
<div id="GLFTR" style="WIDTH: 100%" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#160; </font></div>
</div>

<div id="PN" style="WIDTH: 100%; PAGE-BREAK-AFTER: always">
<div style="WIDTH: 100%; TEXT-ALIGN: right"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">11/11/15&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;The Kroger Co. Confidential&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;3</font></div>

<div style="WIDTH: 100%; TEXT-ALIGN: center">
<hr style="COLOR: indianred" noshade size="2">
</div>
</div>

<div id="HDR">
<div id="GLHDR" style="WIDTH: 100%" align="right"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#160; </font></div>
</div>
</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="royalblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">About The Kroger Co.</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger, one of the <font color="black" style="FONT-SIZE: 13pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">world's</font> largest retailers, employs nearly 400,000 associates who serve customers in 2,623 supermarkets and multi-department stores in 34 states and the District of Columbia under two dozen local banner names including Kroger, City Market, Dillons, Food 4 Less, Fred Meyer, Fry's, Harris Teeter, Jay C, King Soopers, QFC, Ralphs and Smith's. The company also operates 781 convenience stores, 327 fine jewelry stores, 1,350 supermarket fuel centers and 37 food processing plants in the U.S.&#160;&#160;Recognized by Forbes as the most generous company in America, Kroger supports hunger relief, breast cancer awareness, the military and their families, and more than 30,000 schools and community organizations. Kroger contributes food and funds equal to 200 million meals a year through more than 100 Feeding America food bank partners. A leader in supplier diversity, Kroger is a proud member of the Billion Dollar Roundtable and the U.S. Hispanic Chamber's Million Dollar Club.</font></div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="royalblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 13pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Additional Information and Where to Find It</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">The tender offer referenced herein has not yet commenced. This communication is for informational purposes only and is neither an offer to purchase nor a solicitation of an offer to sell shares of Roundy&#8217;s, Inc. (&#8220;Roundy&#8217;s&#8221;), nor is it a substitute for the tender offer materials that The Kroger Co. (&#8220;Parent&#8221;) and KS Merger Sub Inc. (&#8220;Acquisition Sub&#8221;), a wholly-owned subsidiary of Parent, will file with the Securities and Exchange Commission (&#8220;SEC&#8221;) upon commencement of the tender offer. At the time the tender offer is commenced, Parent and Acquisition Sub will file with the SEC tender offer materials on Schedule TO, and Roundy&#8217;s will file with the SEC a Solicitation/Recommendation Statement on Schedule 14D-9, with respect to the tender offer. The tender offer materials (including an Offer to Purchase, a related Letter of Transmittal and certain other tender offer documents) and the Solicitation/Recommendation Statement will contain important information. Holders of shares of Roundy&#8217;s are urged to read these documents carefully when they become available, because they will contain important information that holders of Roundy&#8217;s securities should consider before making any decision regarding tendering their securities. The Offer to Purchase, the related Letter of Transmittal and certain other tender offer documents, as well as the Solicitation/Recommendation Statement, will be made available to all holders of shares of Roundy&#8217;s at no expense to them. The tender offer materials and the Solicitation/Recommendation Statement will be made available for free at the SEC&#8217;s web site at <font color="blue" style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; TEXT-DECORATION: underline; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; DISPLAY: inline">www.sec.gov</font>. Additional copies of the tender offer materials may be obtained at no charge by sending a written request to Parent at The Kroger Co., 1014 Vine Street, Cincinnati, OH 45202-1100, Attention: General Counsel.</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

<div style="DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt">&#160;</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font color="royalblue" style="FONT-SIZE: 13pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; DISPLAY: inline">Forward-<font style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">Looking Statements</font></font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="left"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">This document contains certain forward-looking statements about the future performance of Kroger. These statements are based on management's assumptions and beliefs in light of the information currently available to it. These statements are indicated by words such as "expect," "intend," "guidance,&#8221; &#8220;will" and similar words.&#160; Various uncertainties and other factors could cause actual results to differ materially from those contained in the forward-looking statements. These include the specific risk factors identified in "Risk Factors" and "Outlook" in Kroger&#8217;s annual report on Form 10-K for our last fiscal year and any subsequent filings, as well as the following:</font></div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

<td style="WIDTH: 36pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline"><font style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline"><font style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#9679;</font></font></font></div>
</td>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger&#8217;s ability to achieve sales, earnings and cash flow goals may be affected by: labor negotiations or disputes; changes in the types and numbers of businesses that compete with Kroger; pricing and promotional activities of existing and new competitors, including non-traditional competitors, and the aggressiveness of that competition; Kroger&#8217;s response to these actions; the state of the economy, including interest rates, the inflationary and deflationary trends in certain commodities, and the unemployment rate; the effect that fuel costs have on</font></div>

<div>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
<td style="WIDTH: 36pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">&#160;</font></div>
</td>
<td>
<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">consumer spending; volatility of fuel margins; changes in government-funded benefit programs; manufacturing commodity costs; diesel fuel costs related to Kroger&#8217;s logistics operations; trends in consumer spending; the extent to which Kroger&#8217;s customers exercise caution in their purchasing in response to economic conditions; the inconsistent pace of the economic recovery; changes in inflation or deflation in product and operating costs; stock repurchases; Kroger&#8217;s ability to retain pharmacy sales from third party payors; consolidation in the healthcare industry, including pharmacy benefit managers; Kroger&#8217;s ability to negotiate modifications to multi-employer pension plans; natural disasters or adverse weather conditions; the potential costs and risks associated with potential cyber-attacks or data security breaches; the success of Kroger&#8217;s future growth plans; and the successful integration of Harris Teeter and Roundy&#8217;s.&#160; Kroger&#8217;s ability to achieve sales and earnings goals may also be affected by Kroger&#8217;s ability to manage the factors identified above.</font></div>
</td>
</tr></table>
</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>
</div>

<div>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
<td style="WIDTH: 36pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline"><font style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#9679;</font></font></div>
</td>
<td>
<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger&#8217;s ability to use cash flow to continue to repurchase shares, fund dividends, increase capital investments, and maintain Kroger&#8217;s investment grade debt rating could be affected by unanticipated increases in net total debt, Kroger&#8217;s inability to generate cash flow at the levels anticipated, and Kroger&#8217;s failure to generate expected earnings.</font></div>
</td>
</tr></table>
</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

<div>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
<td style="WIDTH: 36pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline"><font style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline"><font style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#9679;</font></font></font></div>
</td>
<td>
<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger&#8217;s commencement of a tender offer will be contingent upon the merger agreement not being terminated prior to the commencement of the offer.&#160; The requirement to consummate the merger will be contingent upon the merger agreement being in effect and the conditions to the merger being satisfied or waived.&#160; The closing of the transaction could fail to occur before the end of calendar year 2015 if the tender offer does not achieve the anticipated results, if the conditions to closing are not satisfied or are not satisfied in a timely manner, or if the merger agreement is terminated as provided in the agreement.</font></div>
</td>
</tr></table>
</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

<div>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" id="list" width="100%" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman">
<tr valign="top">
<td style="WIDTH: 36pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center">
<div style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline"><font style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; DISPLAY: inline">&#9679;</font></font></div>
</td>
<td>
<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify"><font style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-STYLE: italic; DISPLAY: inline">Kroger&#8217;s ability to finance the transaction with debt will depend on the availability of the debt markets, including commercial paper, our credit facility, and other sources of debt financing.</font></div>
</td>
</tr></table>
</div>

<div style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt" align="justify">&#160;</div>

Please refer to Kroger's reports and filings with the Securities and Exchange Commission for a further discussion of these risks and uncertainties.</font></div>
